# Recommended Tools and Software

**Specific software recommendations for UK trades businesses**

---

## 🎯 Philosophy

**Free/low-cost tools are often perfectly adequate.** You don't need enterprise-grade expensive solutions.

**This guide recommends:**
- Tools actually used by small UK trades businesses
- Options at different price points
- What NorthWest Heating uses (proven to work)

---

## 🔐 Password Managers

### Bitwarden (Recommended for Most)
- **Cost:** Free (personal), £3/user/month (business)
- **Why:** Open source, secure, works on all devices
- **Best for:** Small businesses wanting free/cheap solution
- **UK-based:** No (US), but GDPR compliant
- **NorthWest Heating uses:** Bitwarden free tier

### 1Password
- **Cost:** £6.50/user/month (business)
- **Why:** Very polished, excellent user experience
- **Best for:** If budget allows and you want premium experience
- **UK-based:** No (Canada), but GDPR compliant

### Keeper
- **Cost:** £3.75/user/month
- **Why:** Good middle ground, strong security
- **Best for:** Those wanting paid solution cheaper than 1Password

**Don't use:** Browser-only password saving (not secure enough), Excel spreadsheets, sticky notes

