## 🔒 Antivirus

### Windows Defender (Recommended for Most)
- **Cost:** Free (built into Windows 10/11)
- **Why:** Actually very good, no additional cost
- **Best for:** Small businesses on Windows
- **NorthWest Heating uses:** Windows Defender

### Bitdefender
- **Cost:** ~£25/device/year
- **Why:** Excellent protection, lightweight
- **Best for:** If you want paid solution

### ESET
- **Cost:** ~£30/device/year
- **Why:** Good balance of security and performance
- **Best for:** Alternative to Bitdefender

**Don't need:** Norton, McAfee (bloated, expensive, Windows Defender is fine)

