## ☁️ Cloud Storage & Backup

### OneDrive (Recommended if using Microsoft 365)
- **Cost:** Included with Microsoft 365 (1TB per user)
- **Why:** Integrates with Windows, automatic sync
- **Best for:** Microsoft 365 users
- **NorthWest Heating uses:** OneDrive

### Google Drive
- **Cost:** Included with Google Workspace (30GB-2TB depending on plan)
- **Why:** Integrates with Google Workspace
- **Best for:** Google Workspace users

### Dropbox Business
- **Cost:** £10/user/month (3TB)
- **Why:** Good if not using Microsoft/Google
- **Best for:** Standalone cloud storage need

**Don't use:** Consumer Dropbox/Google Drive for business data (use business versions)

