## 📱 Mobile Device Management

### Find My Device (Android) / Find My iPhone (Recommended for Small Businesses)
- **Cost:** Free (built-in)
- **Why:** Remote locate and wipe capability
- **Best for:** Small businesses (under 10 devices)
- **NorthWest Heating uses:** Find My Device (Samsung phones)

### Microsoft Intune
- **Cost:** From £4.40/user/month
- **Why:** Full MDM solution, integrates with Microsoft 365
- **Best for:** Larger businesses (15+ devices) or complex requirements

**Don't need:** Expensive MDM for small fleet of phones (built-in tools work fine)

