## 🌐 Website and Hosting

### WordPress (CMS) + Reputable Hosting
- **Hosting cost:** £5-15/month (123-reg, SiteGround, etc.)
- **Why:** Popular, flexible, easy to update
- **Best for:** Most trades businesses
- **Security:** Keep WordPress and plugins updated, use security plugins

### Squarespace / Wix
- **Cost:** £10-20/month (all-in-one)
- **Why:** Very easy, no technical knowledge needed
- **Best for:** Simple sites, those who want easy

**Key:** Whatever you use, keep it updated and have SSL certificate (https://)

