## 💳 Payment Processing

### Stripe
- **Cost:** 1.5% + 20p per transaction (online)
- **Why:** Easy to integrate, good features
- **Best for:** Online payments, invoicing
- **NorthWest Heating uses:** Stripe for online payments

### GoCardless
- **Cost:** 1% per transaction (Direct Debit)
- **Why:** Great for recurring payments
- **Best for:** Regular monthly customers

### SumUp / iZettle
- **Cost:** Card reader ~£30, 1.69% per transaction
- **Why:** Simple card payments on-site
- **Best for:** Taking payment at customer sites

**Don't:** Store credit card details yourself (let payment processor handle it)

