## 🎯 Recommendations by Business Size

### 1-5 Employees (Very Small)
- Microsoft 365 Business Basic or Google Workspace
- Xero or QuickBooks
- Bitwarden free
- Windows Defender
- Built-in phone security
- Simple WordPress site
- **~£100-150/month**

### 6-15 Employees (Small - NorthWest Heating)
- Everything above, plus:
- Job management software (Tradify/ServiceM8)
- Consider paid password manager
- External backup drive
