## ❓ Common Questions

**"Should we use free or paid tools?"**
Free tools (Bitwarden free, Windows Defender) are often perfectly adequate. Pay for things where it genuinely adds value (Microsoft 365, Xero, job management).

**"Mac or PC?"**
PCs are fine for trades businesses and cheaper. Macs work but more expensive and some trades-specific software is Windows-only.

**"Android or iPhone for company phones?"**
Both work. Android is cheaper (£150-250 vs £400+), iPhones last longer (5+ years support vs 3-4 years). Pick based on budget.

**"Do we need business-grade everything?"**
Yes for: Email, accounting, cloud storage
No for: Antivirus (Windows Defender fine), backup (OneDrive fine)

